    "description": "Speciality Restaurants is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Bengaluru. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Speciality Restaurants:\nSpeciality Restaurants is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Speciality Restaurants!",
